A cockroach drone is a low levelled creature residing in the bottom and middle level of the Stronghold of Player Safety. They are generally good monsters for training for lower level players, due to their low life points and relatively decent drops for their level. However, cockroach drones are often left alone since the higher levelled cockroaches give more experience and better drops.

Update history[edit | edit source]

This information has been compiled as part of the update history project. Some updates may not be included – see here for how to help out!
  • patch 17 May 2021 (Update):
    • Since the Cockroach Soul can now be added to the Slayer Codex you'll now need to have one for the 'To Be a Master' achievement.
  • hidden 1 March 2021 (Update):
    • Now assignable as a Slayer task by Vannaka, and is now part of the cockroaches Slayer category.
  • ninja 7 August 2017 (Update):
    • Cockroach drones now drop carapace in the cavern beneath the Stronghold of Player Safety.
  • patch 9 February 2011 (Update):
    • Cockroach drones's wings no longer cause their body to become invisible.
  • patch 24 November 2010 (Update):
    • Cockroach drones now appear correctly on hills.
  • update 11 March 2008 (Update):
    • Added to game.
